- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the training and testing of neural networks for the task of horizon detection.
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with seismic data visualization and analysis.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes the usage of neural networks for automated horizon detection.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper discusses the open-sourced research and reproducibility of the model-building process.
